        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer42995370" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12636618620885980651">This is a very difficult book. Not because it is a challenge to read, but because it is a challenge to understand. It is the sort of book that does not comfort, but forces you to question everything about your own life. And so it is a great book, and even a necessary one.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


